大案牍库 — Monorepo Layout (Bun Workspaces)
=============================================

packages/
├── contract/                 @dak/contract — shared API contract
│   ├── package.json
│   ├── tsconfig.json
│   └── src/
│       ├── index.ts          re-exports everything
│       ├── schemas.ts        Zod schemas (Entry, SearchRequest, SearchResponse, IngestRequest …)
│       ├── types.ts          derived TS types via z.infer<>
│       └── routes.ts         route constants & HTTP method definitions
│
├── server/                   @dak/server — Hono API server
│   ├── package.json          deps: hono, minisearch, @dak/contract
│   ├── tsconfig.json
│   ├── Dockerfile            Bun + Litestream multi-stage build
│   ├── litestream.yml        Litestream → R2 备份配置
│   ├── fly.toml              Fly.io 部署配置 (volume mount /data)
│   └── src/
│       ├── index.ts          Hono app bootstrap + Bun.serve
│       ├── routes/
│       │   ├── search.ts     GET  /api/search
│       │   ├── feeds.ts      GET  /api/feeds, GET /api/feeds/:id
│       │   ├── stats.ts      GET  /api/stats
│       │   ├── ingest.ts     POST /api/entries  (api-key-protected)
│       │   └── auth.ts       POST /api/auth/login
│       │                     POST /api/auth/logout
│       │                     GET  /api/auth/me
│       │                     POST /api/api-keys          创建 API key
│       │                     GET  /api/api-keys          列出当前用户 keys
│       │                     DELETE /api/api-keys/:id   撤销 key
│       ├── middleware/
│       │   ├── session.ts    cookie-based session (login 场景)
│       │   └── api-key.ts    Bearer token / X-API-Key header 校验 (SDK/Worker 场景)
│       ├── auth/
│       │   ├── password.ts   argon2 hash + verify
│       │   └── api-key.ts    key 生成 (crypto.randomUUID) + hash 存储 + 前缀匹配
│       ├── search/
│       │   └── engine.ts     MiniSearch index build & query logic
│       ├── db/
│       │   ├── schema.ts     DB table definitions (entries, users, api_keys, sessions)
│       │   ├── client.ts     bun:sqlite client (DB_PATH=/data/dak.db, WAL mode)
│       │   └── migrations/   schema migrations
│       └── static/           built @dak/ui assets (copied at build time)
│
├── ui/                       @dak/ui — React SPA
│   ├── package.json          deps: react, react-dom, @dak/contract
│   ├── tsconfig.json
│   ├── vite.config.ts
│   ├── index.html
│   └── src/
│       ├── main.tsx
│       ├── App.tsx
│       ├── api.ts            typed HTTP client using @dak/contract types
│       ├── router.ts
│       ├── components/
│       └── types.ts          re-exports from @dak/contract
│
├── sdk/                      @dak/sdk — query SDK (npm published)
│   ├── package.json          deps: @dak/contract
│   ├── tsconfig.json
│   ├── tsup.config.ts
│   └── src/
│       ├── index.ts          re-exports search + feeds
│       ├── client.ts         HTTP client (fetch-based, configurable base URL)
│       ├── search.ts         search() wrapper
│       ├── feeds.ts          getFeeds(), getFeedsByCategory(), etc.
│       └── types.ts          re-exports from @dak/contract
│
├── cli/                      @dak/cli — CLI tool (npm published, bin: dak)
│   ├── package.json          deps: @dak/sdk
│   ├── tsconfig.json
│   └── src/
│       ├── index.ts          arg parser + command dispatch
│       ├── commands/
│       │   ├── search.ts     dak search <query> [options]
│       │   ├── feeds.ts      dak feeds [options]
│       │   ├── stats.ts      dak stats
│       │   └── suggest.ts    dak suggest <query>
│       └── output.ts         formatters (table, JSON)
│
└── ingestion-worker/         @dak/ingestion-worker — RSS ingestion worker
    ├── package.json          deps: rss-parser, turndown, @dak/contract
    ├── tsconfig.json
    └── src/
        ├── index.ts          entry point (cron or CLI trigger)
        ├── fetcher.ts        RSS/Atom fetch via rss-parser
        ├── parser.ts         HTML→Markdown (turndown), extract metadata
        ├── dedup.ts          content hash dedup
        ├── uploader.ts       POST entries to @dak/server ingestion API
        └── config/
            ├── sources.yaml  subscription source definitions
            └── categories.yaml

config/                       (root-level, shared config for local dev)
├── .env.example              RSSHUB_BASE_URL, DAK_SERVER_URL, DAK_API_KEY,
│                             R2_ACCESS_KEY, R2_SECRET_KEY, R2_ENDPOINT
└── rsshub/
    └── fly.toml              RSSHub deployment config

skills/                       Claude Code / AI Agent skills
├── dak/
│   └── SKILL.md
└── dak_summary/
    └── SKILL.md

doc/
├── architecture.drawio       system + package architecture diagrams
└── REPO_LAYOUT               this file

daily_summary/                AI-generated daily news summaries
topic_summary/                AI-generated topic analysis reports

package.json                  root — bun workspaces config
tsconfig.json                 root — shared TS config
